<inglise> REGULATION (EEC) No 1683/71 OF THE COMMISSION of 30 July 1971 fixing the conditions for awarding contracts in respect of operations for the processing of tomatoes withdrawn from the market into concentrated tomato pur&eacute;e </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1683/71, milles m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks turult k&otilde;rvaldatud tomatite kontsentreeritud tomatip&uuml;reeks t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisega seotud toiminguid k&auml;sitlevate lepingute s&otilde;lmimise tingimused 30. juuli 1971 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 159/66/EEC 1 of 25 October 1966 laying down additional provisions on the common organisation of the market in fruit and vegetables, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 967/71 2, and in particular Article 7b (4) thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 25. oktoobri 1966. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 159/66/EM&Uuml;, millega n&auml;hakse ette puu- ja k&ouml;&ouml;giviljaturu &uuml;hist korraldust k&auml;sitlevad lisas&auml;tted, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 967/71, (2) eriti selle artikli 7b l&otilde;iget 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas recourse to the option to process products withdrawn from the market, with a view to distributing free of charge products obtained from such processing, was limited by Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1560/70 3 of 31 July 1970 to processing into juice; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni 31. juuli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1560/70 (3) piiratakse v&otilde;imalust t&ouml;&ouml;delda turult k&otilde;rvaldatud tooteid, pidades silmas t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisel saadud toodete tasuta jagamist, k&otilde;nealuste toodete mahlaks t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, if this option seems unlikely to provide sufficient outlets for products withdrawn from the market, provision should be made for processing tomatoes into a product other than juice; </inglise>
<eesti> juhul kui t&otilde;en&auml;oliselt ei pakuta selle v&otilde;imalusega turult k&otilde;rvaldatud toodetele piisavalt turustusv&otilde;imalusi, tuleks s&auml;testada tomatite t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine muudeks toodeteks kui mahl; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the third subparagraph of Article 7b (3) of Regulation No 159/66/EEC provides that contracts for the processing of fruit and vegetables should be granted to industry by a tendering procedure by the agency appointed by the Member State concerned; whereas Regulation (EEC) No 1560/70 specified the procedure for awarding contracts in respect of such operations; whereas it would be appropriate to use that procedure when contracts in respect of the processing operations dealt with in this Regulation are being awarded; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 159/66/EM&Uuml; artikli 7b l&otilde;ike 3 kolmanda l&otilde;iguga n&auml;hakse ette, et puu- ja k&ouml;&ouml;giviljade t&ouml;&ouml;tlemist k&auml;sitlevate lepingute s&otilde;lmimine peaks toimuma pakkumismenetluse teel, mille korraldab asjaomase liikmeriigi poolt m&auml;&auml;ratud asutus; m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 1560/70 m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks selliseid toiminguid k&auml;sitlevate lepingute s&otilde;lmimise kord; oleks asjakohane kasutada k&otilde;nealust korda lepingute s&otilde;lmimisel k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses k&auml;sitletud t&ouml;&ouml;tlemistoimingute suhtes; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Management Committee for Fruit and Vegetables; </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las puu- ja k&ouml;&ouml;giviljaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The processing operations referred to in the fifth indent of (a) in the first subparagraph of Article 7b (1) of Regulation No 159/66/EEC may also apply to the processing of tomatoes into concentrated tomato pur&eacute;e. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse nr 159/66/EM&Uuml; artikli 7b l&otilde;ike 1 esimese l&otilde;igu punkti a viiendas taandes osutatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlemistoiminguid v&otilde;ib kohaldada samuti tomatite kontsentreeritud tomatip&uuml;reeks t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The agency appointed by the Member State concerned shall award these contracts for processing to industry by means of a standing invitation to tender in accordance with the conditions laid down in Articles 2 to 8 of Regulation (EEC) No 1560/70. </inglise>
<eesti> Asjaomase liikmesriigi poolt m&auml;&auml;ratud asutus s&otilde;lmib k&otilde;nealused t&ouml;&ouml;tlemislepingud alalise pakkumismenetluse abil vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1560/70 artiklites 2-8 s&auml;testatud tingimustele. </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of the present Regulation the provisions of that Regulation which refer to juice should be understood as referring to concentrated tomato pur&eacute;e. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse kohaldamisel tuleks k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse s&auml;tetes sisalduvaid viiteid mahlale m&otilde;ista viidetena kontsentreeritud tomatip&uuml;reele. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamisele j&auml;rgneval p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> 1OJ No 192, 27.11.1966, p. 3286/66. 2OJ No 105, 12.5.1971, p. 3. 3OJ No 169, 1.8.1970, p. 59. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 30. juuli 1971 Komisjoni nimel </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 30 July 1971. </inglise>
